<HEADLINE> Sen. Specter Tries Comedy Routine  </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
   PHILADELPHIA (AP) -- Arlen Specter has served on the Warren
Commission, as Philadelphia District Attorney and as U.S. senator.
</P>
<P>
