<HEADLINE> Cheap-Gas Controversy in Mass.  </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
   BRIDGEWATER, Mass. (AP) -- The operator of a gas station who says
he cut prices out of sympathy for consumers hit by spiraling fuel
costs said Friday he's being fired for selling cheap gas.
</P>
